        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p>We stock our service trucks with the most common OEM Kenmore parts for same-day service, including:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2  no-bullet pl-1">
                <span><strong>Drain pumps and hoses</strong></span>
              </li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">
                <span><strong>Water inlet valves</strong></span>
              </li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">
                <span><strong>Drive belts and pulleys</strong></span>
              </li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">
                <span><strong>Motor couplers and assemblies</strong></span>
              </li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">
                <span><strong>Door locks and lid switches</strong></span>
              </li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">
                <span><strong>Electronic control boards</strong></span>
              </li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">
                <span><strong>Suspension rods and dampers</strong></span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">All parts are <strong>factory-certified</strong> for durability, safety, and proper fit.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="page-container" id="anchor-5">
        <div class="header-container">
          <div class="head-content-h">
            <h2>Should You Repair or Replace Your Kenmore Washer?</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p>We'll help you decide based on your machine's condition:</p>
            <ul style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
              <li><strong>Repair</strong> – If your washer is less than 10 years old, in good shape, and the repair cost is under half the price of a new one.</li>
              <li><strong>Replace</strong> – If the washer is over 12 years old, has recurring breakdowns, or needs a major part replacement like a transmission or control board alongside other issues.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Our recommendations are always honest and brand-specific.</p>

            <h3>Typical Repair Costs</h3>
            <p>Your repair fee covers everything it takes to get your washer running again, including:</p>

            <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">Licensed, factory-trained technicians</li>
                <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">Insurance and liability coverage</li>
